1
00:01:27,520 --> 00:01:32,670
[Truth or Dare]

2
00:01:32,670 --> 00:01:34,790
[Episode 20]

3
00:01:34,790 --> 00:01:37,530
[Suspicious Ledgers]

4
00:01:37,530 --> 00:01:39,010
No. This isn't a matter of taking a risk.

5
00:01:39,010 --> 00:01:42,360
- Listen to me. I have to do this.
- Uncle He.
- Otherwise, neither one of us can leave.

6
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:44,140
- Uncle He, listen to me—
- Stop right there!

7
00:01:44,140 --> 00:01:46,140
You damn Boulder-Shattering Chest.

8
00:01:46,140 --> 00:01:48,880
Turns out you've always wanted to run away.

9
00:01:48,880 --> 00:01:50,930
Move aside.

10
00:01:50,930 --> 00:01:54,080
To think I have been treating you as my friend

11
00:01:54,080 --> 00:01:56,130
and trusting your words.

12
00:01:56,130 --> 00:02:00,020
Turns out you've been lying and using me this whole time as if I were a fool!

13
00:02:00,020 --> 00:02:03,730
- I'm sorry Nan Xiang.
- Let me warn you. If you want to treat me as a fool—
- Nan Xiang!

14
00:02:03,730 --> 00:02:05,780
What exactly are you trying to do?

15
00:02:05,780 --> 00:02:09,830
Xiao Bao, she's been lying to us the whole time.

16
00:02:09,830 --> 00:02:12,750
She has wanted to run away this whole time.

17
00:02:12,750 --> 00:02:14,650
She coaxed me into treating her well,

18
00:02:14,650 --> 00:02:16,280
tricked you into marrying her,

19
00:02:16,280 --> 00:02:19,970
and she even wants to steal my dad's map! Liar!

20
00:02:19,970 --> 00:02:23,780
Nan Xiang, I'm warning, stop spouting nonsense.

21
00:02:23,780 --> 00:02:27,250
I know what's true, okay?

22
00:02:27,250 --> 00:02:29,080
Xiao Bao,

23
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:34,150
you'd rather believe an outsider than believe me.

24
00:02:34,150 --> 00:02:37,320
Nan Xiang, can you stop causing trouble? So annoying!

25
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:41,750
Xiao Bao, I do everything for your sake!

26
00:02:41,750 --> 00:02:44,660
Since we were young, I've treated you so well.

27
00:02:45,300 --> 00:02:47,260
Yet for a liar,

28
00:02:47,260 --> 00:02:49,880
you'd rather believe a liar than believe me.

29
00:02:49,880 --> 00:02:52,340
You're even shouting at me.

30
00:02:58,410 --> 00:03:00,800
You liar.

31
00:03:01,750 --> 00:03:04,320
I will find evidence against you for sure.

32
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:07,380
Just wait. Move!

33
00:03:11,900 --> 00:03:14,170
Are you okay, Father-in-Law?

34
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:19,510
You're not hurt, right?

35
00:03:21,180 --> 00:03:25,280
- Xiao Bao.
- I won't let her hurt you guys.

36
00:03:45,650 --> 00:03:47,420
Wanzi,

37
00:03:48,590 --> 00:03:50,920
can I ask you about something?

38
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:55,140
- Go ahead.
- Why exactly did you

39
00:03:55,140 --> 00:03:57,630
steal Godfather's cane?

40
00:04:01,250 --> 00:04:03,690
To find the map.

41
00:04:03,690 --> 00:04:05,880
I want to leave here.

42
00:04:08,340 --> 00:04:10,410
So Nan Xiang wasn't spouting nonsense.

43
00:04:10,410 --> 00:04:13,140
You really want to leave.

44
00:04:13,140 --> 00:04:16,280
Actually, there isn't a map.

45
00:04:17,690 --> 00:04:19,990
If you want to leave here,

46
00:04:21,220 --> 00:04:24,930
you have to get through the formation outside our fort.

47
00:04:24,930 --> 00:04:28,560
You can only leave by figuring out the secret of it.

48
00:04:29,360 --> 00:04:31,780
Of the whole fort, only I,

49
00:04:31,780 --> 00:04:34,960
Nan Xiang, Old Wu, Godfather, and the guide,

50
00:04:34,960 --> 00:04:38,570
the five of us know.

51
00:04:43,900 --> 00:04:47,280
Then that means I can't leave here.

52
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:51,140
I thought you had already...

53
00:04:51,140 --> 00:04:53,790
- Nevermind.
- Xiao Bao,

54
00:04:54,700 --> 00:04:56,460
- I'm sorry.
- Enough.

55
00:04:56,460 --> 00:04:58,550
No need to say anymore.

56
00:04:59,880 --> 00:05:04,090
It's very normal to want to leave here. That's perfectly justified.

57
00:05:04,090 --> 00:05:07,790
I just thought that after such a long time,

58
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:10,730
you'd already gotten used to being here,

59
00:05:12,420 --> 00:05:14,590
gotten used to me.

60
00:05:19,590 --> 00:05:23,720
Xiao Bao, I actually want to leave here because

61
00:05:23,720 --> 00:05:27,420
I really, really don't want you to be in danger for me again.

62
00:05:27,420 --> 00:05:31,770
I also don't want you to be controlled by Nan Batian, making you have to go capture Night-Spirited Hero.

63
00:05:31,770 --> 00:05:36,290
I hope for you to get back on the right path and escape this life sooner.

64
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:40,810
Everything I'm saying is from my heart,

65
00:05:40,810 --> 00:05:42,870
nothing is a lie.

66
00:05:43,420 --> 00:05:45,240
Really?

67
00:05:48,020 --> 00:05:50,310
Also, Xiao Bao,

68
00:05:52,140 --> 00:05:57,480
some things are not as simple as you think.

69
00:05:59,330 --> 00:06:01,980
I only believe what I see.

70
00:06:01,980 --> 00:06:04,830
I know what kind of person you are.

71
00:06:04,830 --> 00:06:06,720
I also know

72
00:06:08,250 --> 00:06:11,240
that you're the person I like most in this world.

73
00:06:16,380 --> 00:06:19,550
Xiao Bao, do you know?

74
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:23,270
I really, really wish

75
00:06:23,820 --> 00:06:27,040
that we could have met

76
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:29,340
at another time and place.

77
00:06:29,340 --> 00:06:31,770
I really wish for that.

78
00:07:26,850 --> 00:07:28,630
Where did this come from?

79
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:34,760
Who is this? It's so ugly.

80
00:07:34,760 --> 00:07:38,070
This is you, Young Master. You can tell just from one glance.

81
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:41,810
You think... this looks like me?

82
00:07:42,580 --> 00:07:45,960
Look at this nose. It's obviously you.

83
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:53,120
Now that you mention it, it really does look like me.

84
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:57,800
Young Master, weren't you just saying it was ugly?

85
00:08:02,410 --> 00:08:04,640
Where is my wife?

86
00:08:05,490 --> 00:08:09,980
[Blessed Treasury Shop]

87
00:08:51,290 --> 00:08:55,790
Jing, wen, zi, hai.
(T/N: some kind of code)

88
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:58,280
What is all this?

89
00:08:58,280 --> 00:09:01,040
Whatever, I'll just take them all.

90
00:09:36,130 --> 00:09:37,490
What are you up to?

91
00:09:37,490 --> 00:09:40,510
All these are ledgers that I stole from Older Brother Situ.

92
00:09:40,510 --> 00:09:41,740
Hurry and look

93
00:09:41,740 --> 00:09:44,130
to see whether they're really related to the sales of contraband salt.

94
00:09:44,130 --> 00:09:47,100
Lest your suspicions.

95
00:09:47,100 --> 00:09:49,680
Don't you believe in your Older Brother Situ?

96
00:09:49,680 --> 00:09:51,270
How come you're stealing ledgers?

97
00:09:51,270 --> 00:09:54,550
I'm tired of you nagging me all the time.

98
00:09:54,550 --> 00:09:59,010
In any case, I took great pains to carry all these here. Look carefully.

99
00:09:59,010 --> 00:10:01,960
Did you do this because you saw something?

100
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,970
How did you know?

101
00:10:06,160 --> 00:10:10,470
It's that... contraband salt gang's leader. Do you still remember him?

102
00:10:10,470 --> 00:10:13,280
I saw him meet with Older Brother Situ.

103
00:10:13,900 --> 00:10:17,880
You're still calling him "Older Brother Situ"?

104
00:10:18,830 --> 00:10:21,760
Situ Lin, all right?

105
00:10:22,820 --> 00:10:26,800
I also hope that Old Brother S— No, Situ Lin, is innocent.

106
00:10:26,800 --> 00:10:31,350
Besides, I believe that he is definitely innocent.

107
00:10:31,350 --> 00:10:35,210
As the chief of the merchants guild, he must know people who do legitimate business as well as those who do illegal business.

108
00:10:35,210 --> 00:10:37,210
If he really is involved,

109
00:10:37,210 --> 00:10:40,160
then you doing this will only alert the enemy.

110
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:41,620
It won't!

111
00:10:41,620 --> 00:10:44,640
He won't be going to the shop these days.

112
00:10:45,430 --> 00:10:48,820
Promise me there's no next time.

113
00:10:48,820 --> 00:10:52,140
Why must you treat it so seriously?

114
00:10:52,140 --> 00:10:54,090
Aren't you going to promise me?

115
00:10:54,980 --> 00:10:57,610
I promise that I'll not dare do it again.

116
00:10:57,610 --> 00:11:01,370
If there's a next time, I won't feed you good food.

117
00:11:01,370 --> 00:11:03,300
That's too cruel!

118
00:11:03,300 --> 00:11:06,590
- I don't believe you.
- I— I believe myself.

119
00:11:06,590 --> 00:11:09,270
Fine, fine. I promise. I promise.

120
00:11:18,850 --> 00:11:21,690
Look at them quickly.

121
00:11:21,690 --> 00:11:24,020
I still have to return them soon.

122
00:11:24,020 --> 00:11:25,790
No need for you to return them. I'll take care of them.

123
00:11:25,790 --> 00:11:27,190
That won't do.

124
00:11:27,190 --> 00:11:29,960
These ledgers need to be put back in their original places.

125
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:33,110
Only I can go. If you go, you'll give us away.

126
00:11:33,110 --> 00:11:37,220
I didn't expect you to be so meticulous, Xiao Wanzi.

127
00:11:39,210 --> 00:11:42,000
All right. Hurry and look at them. I'll come and get them later.

128
00:11:56,460 --> 00:11:58,430
Young Master, what is your order?

129
00:11:58,430 --> 00:12:03,230
Relay this to A'Rou immediately. Tell her that I recently acquired a zither, calligraphy, and painting.

130
00:12:03,230 --> 00:12:05,250
Invite her over to appreciate them.

131
00:12:05,250 --> 00:12:06,910
Yes.

132
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:19,070
Normally, you can't even get a glimpse of her shadow. Yet, the moment she's back, she wants to eat.

133
00:12:19,070 --> 00:12:21,590
Xiao Wanzi is getting out of hand.

134
00:12:21,590 --> 00:12:24,340
It's already great that she's willing to stay and pretend to be the princess.

135
00:12:24,340 --> 00:12:26,420
What else can we ask for?

136
00:12:29,890 --> 00:12:31,970
This way, please, Miss A'Rou.

137
00:12:36,300 --> 00:12:37,950
Qiu Hua!

138
00:12:38,990 --> 00:12:41,660
Why is the woman from Ruyi Restaurant here?

139
00:12:42,540 --> 00:12:46,140
The Prince Consort must be doing whatever he likes because the princess is not here.

140
00:12:46,140 --> 00:12:49,890
What do we do then? It's not like we can chase her away.

141
00:12:53,860 --> 00:12:55,660
Siheng!

142
00:12:56,560 --> 00:12:57,660
Miss Qiao Yun.

143
00:12:57,660 --> 00:13:00,490
What are you here for, Miss A'Rou?

144
00:13:00,490 --> 00:13:04,640
Young Master acquired a zither, calligraphy, and painting and asked Miss A'Rou to look at them together.

145
00:13:04,640 --> 00:13:06,020
Young Master is still waiting.

146
00:13:06,020 --> 00:13:09,070
If there's nothing else, we'll get going.

147
00:13:09,070 --> 00:13:10,340
Then, you should hurry.

148
00:13:10,340 --> 00:13:12,290
Remember to take Miss A'Rou back early.

149
00:13:12,290 --> 00:13:15,010
Or else, it won't be good if the general finds out.

150
00:13:15,010 --> 00:13:16,840
Thanks for the reminder, Miss Qiao Yun.

151
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:19,450
Miss A'Rou, this way, please.

152
00:13:35,820 --> 00:13:39,190
Princess! Princess!

153
00:13:39,190 --> 00:13:41,150
Why are you still sleeping? Something serious has happened.

154
00:13:41,150 --> 00:13:43,100
Come on, Princess.

155
00:13:43,100 --> 00:13:46,120
What serious thing has happened?

156
00:13:46,820 --> 00:13:48,520
Where are my pastries?

157
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:50,590
You're still thinking of food?

158
00:13:50,590 --> 00:13:53,420
That prince consort has brought Miss A'Rou here in the manor.

159
00:13:53,420 --> 00:13:57,150
The two are playing the zither and chatting in the study.

160
00:13:57,700 --> 00:14:01,350
As a fake princess, I can't do anything about the prince consort.

161
00:14:01,350 --> 00:14:02,930
Why can't you do anything?

162
00:14:02,930 --> 00:14:04,590
Go tell the general, okay?

163
00:14:04,590 --> 00:14:07,230
Go tell the general?

164
00:14:07,230 --> 00:14:10,550
But... if things escalate, what good is it to us?

165
00:14:10,550 --> 00:14:13,690
Well, you can't just watch the prince consort bring

166
00:14:13,690 --> 00:14:16,560
t-that kind of woman into the manor.

167
00:14:18,630 --> 00:14:21,990
Look. Before, he only went to the Ruyi Restaurant to meet her.

168
00:14:21,990 --> 00:14:23,750
Now, she's even been brought home.

169
00:14:23,750 --> 00:14:26,660
Then, isn't he going to marry that A'Rou in the future?

170
00:14:26,660 --> 00:14:30,480
He must have had A'Rou come to the manor to discuss the contraband salt matter.

171
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:32,780
I shouldn't interfere.

172
00:14:33,390 --> 00:14:37,330
If by dinnertime, that A'Rou still hasn't come out, bring midnight snacks into there

173
00:14:37,330 --> 00:14:39,000
and then stay in the study.

174
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:42,130
You must see what exactly they're doing, okay?

175
00:14:42,130 --> 00:14:43,920
I won't go.

176
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:46,060
I don't know anything about zithers, chess, calligraphy, and painting.

177
00:14:46,060 --> 00:14:48,360
Why would I stay there?

178
00:14:48,360 --> 00:14:50,760
I'm going back to sleep. You can leave.

179
00:15:05,690 --> 00:15:10,570
[Sophisticated, Lofty Residence]

180
00:15:27,860 --> 00:15:29,920
Aren't they supposed to be playing the zither?

181
00:15:29,920 --> 00:15:32,770
Why isn't there any noise?

182
00:15:39,730 --> 00:15:41,190
Princess?

183
00:15:41,190 --> 00:15:45,290
It turns out... they were really looking at the ledgers.

184
00:15:45,800 --> 00:15:49,330
I came to deliver you some midnight snacks, Husband.

185
00:15:57,230 --> 00:16:00,760
Do you want to take a break and eat?

186
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,990
No need.

187
00:16:06,760 --> 00:16:10,760
How about I take these ledgers back today?

188
00:16:10,760 --> 00:16:12,390
No need. It's already very late.

189
00:16:12,390 --> 00:16:15,430
There are too many ledgers. We won't be able to look through them all any time soon.

190
00:16:15,430 --> 00:16:17,670
Before, didn't you say they weren't useful?

191
00:16:17,670 --> 00:16:20,390
If you look closely, you can find some pieces of evidence.

192
00:16:20,390 --> 00:16:22,390
Let's finish looking through them overnight.

193
00:16:22,390 --> 00:16:24,790
I can help.

194
00:16:26,020 --> 00:16:27,960
I'll help.

195
00:17:00,030 --> 00:17:04,190
Third Young Master, look here. It doesn't match up at all.

196
00:17:18,980 --> 00:17:21,760
How did I fall asleep?

197
00:17:23,260 --> 00:17:25,080
No! A'Rou is still in the study.

198
00:17:25,080 --> 00:17:27,390
How could I fall asleep?

199
00:17:29,600 --> 00:17:31,400
Where are you going?

200
00:17:32,770 --> 00:17:35,190
Why are you here?

201
00:17:35,190 --> 00:17:37,570
Did you undress me?

202
00:17:37,570 --> 00:17:40,730
Qiao Yun did. She just left.

203
00:17:44,330 --> 00:17:46,500
Did you find anything last night?

204
00:17:46,500 --> 00:17:48,990
We didn't find any direct evidence.

205
00:17:49,890 --> 00:17:51,770
- But...
- But!

206
00:17:51,770 --> 00:17:53,830
I found that in Situ Lin's ledgers,

207
00:17:53,830 --> 00:17:56,340
his volume of sales of contraband salt is very low.

208
00:17:56,340 --> 00:17:57,900
Is there a problem with that?

209
00:17:57,900 --> 00:17:59,000
That's a big problem.

210
00:17:59,000 --> 00:18:01,400
Think about it. The gains from selling salt are very profitable.

211
00:18:01,400 --> 00:18:04,930
Why would Situ Lin not do such a profitable business?

212
00:18:04,930 --> 00:18:08,100
Furthermore, he's the chief of the Qingzhou Merchant Guild.

213
00:18:08,100 --> 00:18:10,530
If he wants to monopolize the market, it's very easy for him.

214
00:18:10,530 --> 00:18:13,460
If something is abnormal, there must be a demon.

215
00:18:13,460 --> 00:18:18,160
It seems that there is really something wrong with Older Brother Situ.

216
00:18:20,330 --> 00:18:22,870
Why are you unhappy after you have made contributions?

217
00:18:22,870 --> 00:18:27,430
If Older Brother Situ is a bad guy, of course, I'm unhappy.

218
00:18:29,200 --> 00:18:31,880
Enough. Stop overthinking.

219
00:18:34,770 --> 00:18:36,990
Are you hungry? Let's go eat something.

220
00:18:36,990 --> 00:18:38,760
But I have no appetite.

221
00:18:38,760 --> 00:18:41,110
I'll personally cook. Do you still not have an appetite?

222
00:18:41,110 --> 00:18:42,450
You?

223
00:18:42,450 --> 00:18:44,580
Me. What's so hard about it?

224
00:18:44,580 --> 00:18:47,000
I'll show you my cooking skills.

225
00:18:50,790 --> 00:18:52,740
Will what you make be edible?

226
00:18:52,740 --> 00:18:54,740
Of course.

227
00:18:54,740 --> 00:18:58,090
I'm going to cook now. Hurry and assist me. Start the fire.

228
00:18:58,090 --> 00:19:01,920
Do you know how to start the fire? First, fold the branches in half before you...

229
00:19:02,670 --> 00:19:04,940
No. Don't. Don't do that.

230
00:19:04,940 --> 00:19:07,770
There's smoke everywhere!

231
00:19:11,360 --> 00:19:14,840
You even said you knew how to cook! I almost lost my life!

232
00:19:14,840 --> 00:19:16,020
Didn't we say that

233
00:19:16,020 --> 00:19:17,430
you'll manage the fire and I'll cook?

234
00:19:17,430 --> 00:19:19,980
- There's a fire!
- Princess. Prince Consort.

235
00:19:19,980 --> 00:19:22,730
- Put out the fire.
- Yes, put out the fire.

236
00:19:22,730 --> 00:19:26,510
I-I don't know how to start a fire.

237
00:19:26,510 --> 00:19:28,380
Didn't y-you...

238
00:19:28,380 --> 00:19:31,300
How could you not know how to start a fire?

239
00:19:31,300 --> 00:19:35,300
Wait. You don't know how to start a fire. Why should I know?

240
00:19:35,300 --> 00:19:39,600
I-I'm a dignified junior general. Why would I need to know that? Look at your messy face,

241
00:19:39,600 --> 00:19:40,890
like a little tabby cat.

242
00:19:40,890 --> 00:19:43,400
You're talking about me but aren't you the same?

243
00:19:43,400 --> 00:19:46,970
- Promise me you won't cook ever again. All right?
- Fine.

244
00:19:46,970 --> 00:19:50,690
However, you have to promise me you won't do dangerous things ever again.

245
00:19:50,690 --> 00:19:54,320
I got it. Once I return Situ Lin's ledgers,

246
00:19:54,320 --> 00:19:56,950
I won't care about the matter anymore.

247
00:19:56,950 --> 00:20:00,100
Okay! You said so yourself, little tabby cat.

248
00:20:14,690 --> 00:20:16,390
[Blessed Treasury Shop]

249
00:20:20,770 --> 00:20:24,650
If there's danger, immediately open a window and I'll come and get you right away.

250
00:20:24,650 --> 00:20:26,700
- Don't worry.
- Wait.

251
00:20:27,400 --> 00:20:31,020
I got it. If there's danger, I'll open the window to ask for help.

252
00:20:31,020 --> 00:20:32,260
