00:21:00,550 --> 00:21:02,220
Older Brother Situ.

258
00:21:02,220 --> 00:21:04,610
Why are you here?

259
00:21:04,610 --> 00:21:07,010
I need to see you about something urgent.

260
00:21:07,010 --> 00:21:10,190
I-I didn't see you downstairs so I came up here.

261
00:21:11,180 --> 00:21:12,980
Is that so?

262
00:21:13,850 --> 00:21:15,680
It's so hot.

263
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:19,090
I'll open a window to get some air.

264
00:21:19,090 --> 00:21:22,400
- I happen to have something to talk to you about.
- What is it?

265
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:26,070
Recently, I've come across some difficulties.

266
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:29,180
Wang Biao, who sells contraband salt, keeps forcing me to sell it.

267
00:21:29,180 --> 00:21:31,840
These people are atrocious for the sake of money.

268
00:21:31,840 --> 00:21:33,730
I didn't want to associate with them

269
00:21:33,730 --> 00:21:36,460
but I can't afford to offend them.

270
00:21:36,460 --> 00:21:39,200
So, you don't do salt business because of that?

271
00:21:39,200 --> 00:21:41,080
Yes.

272
00:21:41,080 --> 00:21:45,180
I-I saw that salt...

273
00:21:45,180 --> 00:21:48,360
Your shop doesn't sell much salt.

274
00:21:48,360 --> 00:21:50,410
The salt market in Qingzhou is very complicated.

275
00:21:50,410 --> 00:21:53,800
Although I'm the chief, I cannot do anything about it.

276
00:21:53,800 --> 00:21:56,970
I can't help but be targeted by them.

277
00:21:56,970 --> 00:21:58,930
Older Brother Situ, don't be afraid.

278
00:21:58,930 --> 00:22:02,570
Even though the officials can't deal with them, we still have Night-Spirited Hero.

279
00:22:02,570 --> 00:22:04,580
The Night-Spirited Hero will protect you for sure.

280
00:22:04,580 --> 00:22:06,050
Night-Spirited Hero?

281
00:22:06,050 --> 00:22:07,780
He's now wanted by both officials and criminals.

282
00:22:07,780 --> 00:22:10,350
He's like a clay Bodhisattva crossing a river, he can barely save himself.

283
00:22:10,350 --> 00:22:12,170
How can he protect me?

284
00:22:12,170 --> 00:22:14,840
It's all because of those contraband salt dealers.

285
00:22:14,840 --> 00:22:18,150
They framed him. That's why

286
00:22:18,150 --> 00:22:20,890
