287
00:22:20,890 --> 00:22:24,530
However, don't worry. The Night-Spirited Hero definitely can defeat those bad people.

288
00:22:24,530 --> 00:22:26,390
You trust him so much.

289
00:22:26,390 --> 00:22:29,360
Looks like you have a close relationship with him.

290
00:22:29,360 --> 00:22:31,050
No, no.

291
00:22:31,050 --> 00:22:34,180
It's just that... h-he's the Night-Spirited Hero.

292
00:22:34,180 --> 00:22:39,220
Well, he punishes evil and his fame is widely known. I admire him very much.

293
00:22:39,220 --> 00:22:42,750
That's why I know of his affairs.

294
00:22:42,750 --> 00:22:47,010
All right. I hope that the Night-Spirited Hero can help me past this difficulty.

295
00:22:47,010 --> 00:22:52,490
- Certainly. Older Brother Situ, you get back to work. I have something urgent to tend to so I'm leaving now.
- Okay.

296
00:23:04,750 --> 00:23:08,890
That's right. It's she who surprise attacked us with the Night-Spirited Hero.

297
00:23:08,890 --> 00:23:13,770
The wife of the junior general and Night-Spirited Hero are together?

298
00:23:15,230 --> 00:23:19,240
How interesting. How interesting.

299
00:23:19,900 --> 00:23:24,230
[Blessed Treasury Shop]

300
00:23:35,510 --> 00:23:39,930
That scared me to death. I a-actually ran into Older Brother Situ.

301
00:23:39,930 --> 00:23:43,800
- And then?
- Nothing happened. However, I found out

302
00:23:43,800 --> 00:23:47,660
that person who sells contraband salt is not in collusion with Older Brother Situ.

303
00:23:47,660 --> 00:23:51,480
They met with Older Brother Situ to threaten him into selling contraband salt with them.

304
00:23:52,000 --> 00:23:53,850
There's such a thing?

305
00:23:53,850 --> 00:23:57,810
Hence, Older Brother Situ most likely is not a bad person.

306
00:24:03,480 --> 00:24:07,410
You believe he's innocent? He's such a pretentious person.

307
00:24:07,410 --> 00:24:10,410
Of course, I hope he's not a bad person.

308
00:24:10,410 --> 00:24:12,480
If he's really a victim,

309
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:15,440
then didn't we falsely accuse him before?

310
00:24:17,000 --> 00:24:18,690
You.

311
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:23,300
In any case, you need to promise me something.

312
00:24:23,300 --> 00:24:24,660
What?

313
00:24:24,660 --> 00:24:27,540
Before we get to the bottom of this,

314
00:24:27,540 --> 00:24:30,020
you are not allowed to see Situ Lin.

315
00:24:32,800 --> 00:24:36,430
- Do you hear me?
- I got it. I promise you.

316
00:24:36,430 --> 00:24:38,400
That is more like it.

317
00:25:07,420 --> 00:25:09,590
Boulder Shattering Chest,

318
00:25:09,590 --> 00:25:11,750
don't blame me.

319
00:25:33,280 --> 00:25:35,200
- Xiao Bao.
- Hey, Wanzi.

320
00:25:35,200 --> 00:25:37,620
I brought midnight snacks for you.

321
00:25:37,620 --> 00:25:39,260
Let's go.

322
00:26:04,170 --> 00:26:07,000
Xiao Bao, what are you looking for?

323
00:26:07,000 --> 00:26:10,320
I think I saw Nan Xiang come in here earlier.

324
00:26:10,320 --> 00:26:13,550
I suspect she might've stolen something.

325
00:26:13,550 --> 00:26:16,380
No way. You must've seen wrong.

326
00:26:16,380 --> 00:26:18,270
Your eyes were blurred.

327
00:26:21,470 --> 00:26:24,150
I still think something is not right.

328
00:26:24,150 --> 00:26:27,030
No way. Why would Nan Xiang come to my room?

329
00:26:27,030 --> 00:26:29,140
That's true.

330
00:26:29,140 --> 00:26:31,930
Wanzi, hurry and taste the food I brought you.

331
00:26:31,930 --> 00:26:33,470
Okay.

332
00:26:35,500 --> 00:26:37,830
It smells so good.

333
00:26:41,280 --> 00:26:43,390
What's wrong, Xiao Bao?

334
00:26:47,140 --> 00:26:48,740
Xiao Bao!

335
00:27:01,460 --> 00:27:04,140
This is not good. He's been poisoned. We need to hurry and find the antidote.

336
00:27:04,140 --> 00:27:06,260
Or else, his life will be in danger.

337
00:27:07,280 --> 00:27:09,120
Poisoned?

338
00:27:09,120 --> 00:27:11,610
Where do I go to find the antidote?

339
00:27:13,400 --> 00:27:17,200
Brother Six, it had to be Nan Xiang. It had to be.

340
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:19,410
I'll go find her now.

341
00:27:27,030 --> 00:27:29,240
Considering the time,

342
00:27:29,240 --> 00:27:32,570
the poison should have already taken effect.

343
00:27:33,410 --> 00:27:37,000
I've finally gotten rid of her. I'm exhausted.

344
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,570
Nan Xiang.

345
00:27:39,850 --> 00:27:43,230
You— W-Why are you here?

346
00:27:43,230 --> 00:27:44,540
Where's the antidote?

347
00:27:44,540 --> 00:27:48,160
What antidote? I don't know.

348
00:27:48,160 --> 00:27:52,010
I'm only able to stand here in one piece is because Xiao Bao got poisoned on my behalf.

349
00:27:52,010 --> 00:27:53,910
Xiao Bao?

350
00:27:54,650 --> 00:27:56,010
Where are you going?

351
00:27:56,010 --> 00:27:58,160
Xiao Bao! Xiao Bao!

352
00:27:58,160 --> 00:28:00,230
You, go away!

353
00:28:00,230 --> 00:28:01,890
Xiao Bao.

354
00:28:02,940 --> 00:28:05,230
Xiao Bao, are you okay?

355
00:28:06,260 --> 00:28:09,290
Xiao Bao, I'm sorry.

356
00:28:09,290 --> 00:28:13,420
I didn't do it on purpose. I didn't want to kill you.

357
00:28:14,600 --> 00:28:18,320
I merely wanted to kill this boulder-shattering person.

358
00:28:19,270 --> 00:28:22,680
Nan Xiang, hurry and get the antidote. If not, he'll really die.

359
00:28:22,680 --> 00:28:25,710
Antidote. Where is it?

360
00:28:33,980 --> 00:28:35,900
I don't have it.

361
00:28:40,230 --> 00:28:42,280
Nan Xiang...

362
00:28:43,820 --> 00:28:50,120
Why do you insist on not getting along with Xiao Wanzi?

363
00:28:51,740 --> 00:28:53,530
Xiao Bao,

364
00:28:54,430 --> 00:28:57,400
you're about to die,

365
00:28:59,100 --> 00:29:03,930
yet you're still protecting her?

366
00:29:04,650 --> 00:29:09,100
Xiao Bao.
- Nan Xiang.
- Don't speak to me.

367
00:29:11,330 --> 00:29:13,560
As long as you get the antidote,

368
00:29:13,560 --> 00:29:16,040
I will do anything you want me to.

369
00:29:16,810 --> 00:29:19,410
Will you agree to do anything I say?

370
00:29:22,450 --> 00:29:24,450
Fine.

371
00:29:24,450 --> 00:29:27,600
As long as Xiao Bao agrees to marry me,

372
00:29:29,290 --> 00:29:32,120
I'll give him the antidote.

373
00:29:40,480 --> 00:29:42,150
Xiao Bao,

374
00:29:42,820 --> 00:29:45,510
as long as you agree to marry me,

375
00:29:46,520 --> 00:29:49,110
I'll give you the antidote immediately.

376
00:29:51,750 --> 00:29:53,770
Xiao Bao,

377
00:29:56,520 --> 00:29:59,130
as long as you are willing,

378
00:29:59,130 --> 00:30:02,340
I'll give you the antidote immediately. All right?

379
00:30:02,340 --> 00:30:04,250
Xiao Bao.

380
00:30:10,120 --> 00:30:12,180
Xiao Bao.

381
00:30:14,630 --> 00:30:19,370
I will only marry Xiao Wanzi.

382
00:30:19,370 --> 00:30:21,460
Xiao Bao.

383
00:30:24,940 --> 00:30:28,390
Turns out you hate me that much.

384
00:30:45,280 --> 00:30:46,980
Xiao Bao.

385
00:30:48,260 --> 00:30:52,960
Xiao Bao. Xiao Bao.

386
00:30:52,960 --> 00:30:56,600
As long as you're okay, as long as she can save you,

387
00:30:56,600 --> 00:31:00,900
