394
00:31:40,090 --> 00:31:43,530
From what I see, the sales of wine are not bad.

395
00:31:43,530 --> 00:31:46,700
How about you two continue working and I'll go outside for some air?

396
00:31:46,700 --> 00:31:49,640
Don't go far. I'll be done soon.

397
00:31:56,620 --> 00:31:59,480
How is the investigation into Situ Lin's affairs going?

398
00:31:59,480 --> 00:32:01,650
Situ Lin is usually very careful.

399
00:32:01,650 --> 00:32:03,790
It is very difficult to investigate his background.

400
00:32:03,790 --> 00:32:05,940
I was only able to find out that he is an orphan.

401
00:32:05,940 --> 00:32:08,580
Since young, he grew up in Qingzhou City.

402
00:32:08,580 --> 00:32:10,640
Ten years ago, he went away to do business.

403
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:13,730
